               <provenance>Habta Māryām and ʿAqba Mikāʾel are mentioned
                     in supplication formulas until the end of the month Gǝnbot (3r-105v); the latter name appears in variants: ʿƎqʷǝba
                     Mikāʾel (e.g., 4vb), ʿAqʷǝba Mikāʾel (6ra, 8vc, 47vc, 55ra), ʿUqʷǝba Mikāʾel (10vac, 12vb, 23rc, 33vb), ʿAqba Mikāʾel (the most
                     common spelling from 37vc onwards). 
 Walda
                     Dāwit and Tǝnśāʾe Krǝstos are mentioned in supplication formulas from the month
                     Sane until the end of the Ms. (106r-217r)
                     and in the colophon (217rb).</provenance></history>
